2a:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","em",null,{"children":["Generates a production-quality OpenAPI 3.2 document from the extracted SDK types.  The document is populated with: - An ",["$","code",null,{"children":"info"}]," block sourced from the config or reasonable defaults. - A ",["$","code",null,{"children":"components.schemas"}]," section with one schema per exported type. - ",["$","code",null,{"children":"tags"}]," derived from unique source file paths (grouping by file). - Visibility filtering: ",["$","code",null,{"children":"@internal"}]," symbols are never emitted. - HTTP paths are extracted from ",["$","code",null,{"children":"@route"}]," tags and appropriately mapped."]}]}]
